Savage

Savage looked at Strier's fallen body. He was about to finish him 
off, when Tamron called to him.

"No Savage! Not yet. Look who we have. Remember your memories! This 
is the girl at the valley. The one he loves. Think of the agony you 
could cause him"

Savage recalls this and walks away. his simple mind didn't completly 
understand the idea, but he has to follow orders.

(Be back in a bit, got some stuff to do.)
